name: Agent
line: What's up Rick!

name: Rick
line: Morty, stop! You're not allowed to interpret the will of the heads!

name: Agent
line: What the hell?

name: Rick
line: M-m-my God!

name: Agent
line: Rick, what the hell is wrong with you?

name: Rick
line: It's a figure of speech, Morty. I'm not being coy about anything. If you get what I want you to do, stay out of this.

name: Agent
line: You're the one that keeps dragging these deaths on. You're a walking burlap sack filled with turds.

name: Rick
line: What? What kind of God lets these things happen?

name: Agent
line: One that rewards cruelty and vindictive behavior and doesn't threaten anyone.

name: Rick
line: Okay, fine. I'll bite the bullet, Morty, but only if you give me an hour or so to figure this out.

name: Agent
line: Oh, for God's sake, Rick. I-I'm trying to figure out why you would do this. I hope it involves a gun.

name: Rick
line: Because I want to shoot nobody.

name: Agent
line: Why are you acting like that's not you?!

name: Rick
line: Because you're stupid and I want a quicker death.

name: Agent
line: I-I want to die slowly, like, slowly.

name: Rick
line: Rick! You want to see what a hero Rick is?

name: Agent
line: I want you back!

name: Rick
line: You want to be a real hero, Morty!

name: Agent
line: I hope you get to see the big payoff, Morty

name: Rick
line: I mean, you're not gonna die for real cheap pills, Morty?

name: Agent
line: Oh! I'm gonna die, Morty...
